sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    actor Admin
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant Email as Resend Email

    User->>Browser: Navigate to "Contact Us" page
    User->>Browser: Fill form (name, email, message)
    Browser->>API: POST /api/contact
    Note right of Browser: { name, email, message }
    API->>Email: Send contact email to Paladin team
    Email-->>Admin: Contact form submission
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK
    Browser-->>User: "Message sent successfully"
